# SBA 308A - Crypto Info Website

This project is a simple web application that displays real-time cryptocurrency prices, news, and a list of the top 20 coins by volume. It uses external APIs to fetch data for Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), and Binance Coin (BNB), and updates dynamically on the page.

## Features

- Display current cryptocurrency prices in USD, EUR, and JPY.
- Show a list of the top 20 cryptocurrencies by trading volume.
- Fetch and display the latest crypto news.
- Fetch coin signals
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS and DaisyUI for UI components.

## Technologies

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS (Tailwind CSS, DaisyUI)
- **JavaScript Framework:** Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- **HTTP Requests:** Axios
- **Cryptocurrency Data API:** [CryptoCompare API](https://min-api.cryptocompare.com)
- **News API:** [CryptoCompare News API](https://min-api.cryptocompare.com/documentation#news)
